25.sl:
je rekel:
 »Preklet bodi Kánaan;
 bodi hlapec hlapcev svojih bratov!«

25.en:
He said,
 “Cursed be Canaan;
 A servant of servants will he be to his brothers.”

26.sl:
Potem je rekel:
 »Blagoslovljen Gospod, Semov Bog; 
 Kánaan mu bodi za hlapca!

26.en:
He said,
 “Blessed be Yahweh, the God of Shem;
 Let Canaan be his servant.

27.en:
God enlarge Japheth,
 Let him dwell in the tents of Shem;
 Let Canaan be his servant.”

4.sl:
Nestalen kakor voda, ne boš prvi,
 ker si legel na posteljo svojega očeta;
 takrat si oskrunil moje ležišče.

4.en:
Boiling over as water, you shall not have the pre-eminence;
 Because you went up to your father’s bed;
 Then defiled it. He went up to my couch.

6.en:
My soul, don’t come into their council;
 My glory, don’t be united to their assembly;
 For in their anger they killed a man,
 In their self-will they hamstrung an ox.

8.en:
“Judah, your brothers will praise you:
 Your hand will be on the neck of your enemies;
 Your father’s sons will bow down before you.

22.en:
“Joseph is a fruitful vine,
 A fruitful vine by a spring;
 His branches run over the wall.

27.sl:
Benjamin je volk, ki trga;
 zjutraj požira plen,
 zvečer razdeljuje ulov.«
